postcontent: This is a nice MKE 380 auto pistol. It's a 7+1 capacity.  That's 1 more then the ruger/taurus/diamondback/kel-tec/hellcat style pocket pistols.This is a variant to the Walther PPK pistols. James Bond style. This gun is in very nice condition. Blue slide with a brownish color frame. Comes with a nice leather belt holster. Like I say perfect concealed carry gun. title: For Sale:  Kimber Rimfire Super 22lr
postcontent: The Kimber Rimfire Super is a high quality firearm. It is a full-sized replica of the 1911, even down to the 5" barrel. The fit and finish is top-notch, as should be expected of a pistol in this price range. All functions are the same as a 1911, grip safety and ambidextrous safety. The pistol has had no FTF or malfunctions while firing CCI Velocitor ammo; and is very accurate. My only wish is that the weight and construction materials had been the same as a full-sized 1911. The Rimfire Super is constructed of all aluminum and is therefore very light. This might be a plus for a young person, but for a firearm to practice with, it lacks the heft of the .45ACP 1911s. Even the 10-round magazine is made out of plastic. At least the grip panels are wood. Overall this is a high quality firearm, and I would recommend it to anyone looking for a quality .22 that replicates the full-sized 1911 in every way except weight.  You can Text Or Call me on REDACTED.(Text Preferred).

These are very similar to the HK High Reliability Steel mags, but at a much better price. These are, in every way, far, far superior to C-Products magazines.

Shipping is via Priority - I am offering a discounted flat rate of $5 for up to 4 magazines, and $10 for 5 or more.
